# Contracts — {{PROJECT}}

> This file is yours (project-owned). It is the live contract register —
> inbound + outbound agreements, one entry per contract. `/contract add`
> files a row; `/contract update` advances its status; `/renewals` reads the
> `expiry_date` + `renewal` fields. Don't rewrite history — advance a
> contract's `status` in place, and mark ended contracts `expired` /
> `terminated` (never delete). Format reference: `.claude/contracts-rules.md`.

**Account handle:** every contract references its customer by a stable
`@acct-<slug>` handle (the join key shared across the business-ops modules).
**Money:** always a `value` + `currency` pair. **Dates:** always absolute
(`YYYY-MM-DD`). **`CON-NNN`:** monotonic, never reused.

